Package com.peyrona.mingle.updater

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileComparator
    Strategy interface for comparing local and remote files.
    FileDiscoveryStrategy
    Strategy interface for discovering files that need to be checked/updated.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackupManager
    Manages backup creation and cleanup for files being updated.
    CatalogFileDiscoveryStrategy
    File discovery strategy using catalog.json.
    CatalogParser
    Utility class for parsing catalog.json content.
    CatalogParser.CatalogFileEntry
    Represents a file entry from catalog.json.
    FileComparator.ComparisonContext
    Context for file comparison.
    FileComparator.ComparisonResult
    Result of file comparison.
    FileDiscoveryStrategy.FileEntry
    Represents a file entry with path and optional expected hash.
    FileUpdateOperation
    Encapsulates the file update operation: backup, download, and verify.
    GitHubApiClient
    Client for interacting with GitHub API to fetch file information and content.
    GitHubApiClient.GitHubFileResponse
    Response object for GitHub file metadata.
    GitHubFileUpdater
    Core logic for checking and updating files from GitHub repository.
    HashCalculator
    Utility class for calculating SHA-1 and SHA-256 hashes of files.
    HashFileComparator
    File comparator using hash comparison only.
    TraversalFileDiscoveryStrategy
    File discovery strategy using directory traversal.
    Updater
    Main class for checking and updating files from GitHub repository.
